				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">All load or arithmetic instructions affect the Zero and Negative flags.
<br />
<br />Think of the negative flag is being a copy of the most significant bit (leftmost bit).
<br />The Zero flag is set any time the result is zero.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Here come the fortune cookies!  Here come the fortune cookies!  They're wearing paper hats!</div>
